Mid 80's BBS message boards, imitative of "thirty lashes with a wet noodle" only stinkier. Almost certainly from Monty Python's [[w:The Fish-Slapping Dance|The Fish-Slapping Dance]] (1972) although the fish in that sketch was a [[halibut]].

